race.description: Sportsbet Bet With Mates Maiden Plate
race.comment: DEBRALEE (7) makes her return after 455 days. Usually they need a run but she owns two sharp trial wins in readiness and this doesn't appear to be a deep contest. Can make the perfect return. COSMO DIVA (6) jumped out well in readiness to her first-up attempt but was only sound. Is sure to have come on with that run under her belt but will need some luck from the draw. ROOMERHASIT (5) was much better last time when doing his best work to earn a minor placing at huge odds. Strips fitter and deserves a lot more respect this time. STARNOVA (3) didn't make an impression in his debut prep but returns for a new stable and takes benefit from a jumpout. Can play a role.
